(-7061,'You\'ve got my attention, dragon. You\'ll find I\'m not as easily scared as the villagers below',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,1,0,25,'c17651 Image of Medivh - q9645'),
(-7062,'Your dabbling in the arcane has gone too far, Medivh. You\'ve attracted the attention of powers beyond your understanding. You must leave Karazhan at once!',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,1,0,0,'c17652 Image of Arcanagos - q9645'),
