(-7066,'You leave me no alternative. I will stop you by force if you won\'t listen to reason!',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,1,0,0,'c17652 Image of Arcanagos - q9645'),
(-7067,'Image of Medivh begins to cast a spell of great power, weaving his own essence into the magic.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,2,0,0,'c17651 Image of Medivh - q9645'),
(-7068,'What have you done, wizard? This cannot be! I\'m burning from... within!',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,1,0,0,'c17652 Image of Arcanagos - q9645'),
